Dear Sir/Madam.

As you are aware, {!pocPackage.CFG_French_Office_Name__c} is processing {!pocPackage.BankNameWiseCompanyName} insolvent accounts. Our records show that we have sent a proof of claim but not yet received a letter of release.

Please see the attached letter from {!pocPackage.BankNameWiseCompanyName} for more information.

Sincerely


{!pocPackage.CFG_French_Office_Name__c}

P:{!pocPackage.CFG_Office_Phone_Number__c} E: {!pocPackage.CFG_Office_Email_Address__c}
